JLH Represents in New Orleans for AJLI’s Annual Conference

President Erika Brenneman and President-Elect Rachel Jones represented the Junior League of Harrisburg at the Association of Junior Leagues International (AJLI) Annual Conference this year in New Orleans. While sporting green for mental health awareness the “Be Good to You” campaign was announced to launch as a national initiative in this coming League Year! Other…

Over 9,000 Diapers Packed!

On Saturday, January 13th, Junior League of Harrisburg volunteers packed 9,321 diapers at Healthy Steps Diaper Bank! Healthy Steps is on a mission to empower families and individuals throughout South Central PA to thrive by providing a reliable and adequate source of diapers and period products.
